name: LOTUS x Gaunty 2011
description:
This is the very latest LOTUS limited edition tee.
Only 50 of these will ever be made in this crispy colourway.
We plan to do one of these tees with art from Gaunty every year...maybe every collection even. 
This is the first and will come with a high quality frame-able print of the tee art.

FREE SHIPPING IN NEW ZEALAND

Please note: the price is in NZD so it should be cheapish where ever you live.

name: Cant Stop
description:
there is kinda two ways to read this tee:
- "cant stop wont stop" as a personal ideology
or
-"cant stop wont stop LOTUS" as our threat to haters as a brand.

either way i like it! lol

name: FIGHT THE POWER
description: A LOTUS tribute to Public Enemy. The song "fight the power" is 20 years old this year and this tee design is based on the tee that alot of the crowd in the video are wearing. google it...its a great video. check the LOTUS blog for more images.... get this very limited tee now as there will only ever be 30 of these made and over half are already gone! SHIPPING IS FREE anywhere in the world! The price is in NZD (tees come to you all the way from Wellington, New Zealand)

name: LOTUS Pins
description:
Tera is famous....supremely famous.

Free shipping and a sticker to anywhere in the world from here in New Zealand!

if you are the first person to send us a pic of you wearing your pin will win a free LOTUS Cartel tee! (LOTUS Cartel tees are not for sale and cant be bought. they are for crew only)

so thats basicly $2 for a pin and a tee!
